## What the repo is right now

Pantheon is currently **not one clean runnable app**.

It is a **hybrid corpus**:

```text
1. runnable/semi-runnable code
2. implementation sketches
3. architecture specs
4. daemon/operator doctrine
5. whitepapers/theorems
6. mythic/narrative compression layers
7. personal/cultural notes
8. duplicated/overlapping canon
```

That actually matches your theory: plain language as an AI-legible semantic programming layer.

